{"favorite_id": 10073, "calc_type": "", "dosing": false, "full_title_en": "Geneva Risk Score for Venous Thromboembolism (VTE) Prophylaxis", "short_title_en": "Geneva Score (VTE Prophylaxis)", "medium_description_en": "<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9f5bfad8-fc6b-2952-2485-ed38f1fa9670\">Predicts need for VTE prophylaxis in admitted patients.</span>", "short_description_en": "Inpatient VTE prophylaxis.", "before_use": "", "instructions_en": "<p>Note: this score is different from the <calculator id=\"1750\">Geneva Score (Revised) for PE</calculator>, which <em>diagnoses</em> PE in patients presenting with relevant signs and symptoms.</p>", "purpose_en": ["Prognosis", "Treatment"], "disease_en": ["Deep Venous Thrombosis", "Pulmonary Embolism", "VTE"], "specialty_en": ["Cardiology", "Critical Care", "Hospitalist Medicine", "Internal Medicine", "Surgery (General)", "Surgery (Vascular)"], "chief_complaint_en": ["Chest Pain", "Dyspnea", "Extremity Edema", "Shortness of Breath"], "system_en": ["Cardiac", "Vascular"], "search_abbreviation_en": ["Geneva risk score", "inpatient VTE risk", "VTE prophylaxis", "Thromboprophylaxis", "VTE"], "slug": "geneva-risk-score-venous-thromboembolism-vte-prophylaxis", "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The Geneva Risk Score for VTE Thromboprophylaxis assess inpatients\u2019 risk of VTE to thromboprophylaxis. ", "keywords_en": "Geneva risk score, VTE, thromboprophylaxis, inpatient VTE, VTE risk"}, "content": {"how_to_use": {"use_case_en": "", "pearls_pitfalls_en": "", "why_use_en": "<p>Wide variation exists in the proportion of patients in a given institution who are given VTE prophylaxis (29-89% range in one study, <a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/epdf/10.1111/j.1538-7836.2006.01818.x\" target=\"_blank\">Chopard 2006</a>). This&nbsp;score can help institutions and individuals make evidence-based decisions on who is&nbsp;at sufficiently low risk for VTE so as to avoid unnecessary prophylaxis.</p>"}, "next_steps": {"advice_en": "<p>As with any clinical decision tool, use your judgment when making therapeutic decisions.&nbsp;</p>", "management_en": "", "critical_actions_en": ""}, "about": {"formula_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Addition of the selected points:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"224\" /><col width=\"67\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Points</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cardiac failure</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Respiratory failure</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Recent stroke (&lt;3 months ago)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Recent myocardial infarction (&lt;4 weeks ago)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Acute infectious disease (including sepsis)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Acute rheumatic disease</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Active malignancy</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Myeloproliferative syndrome</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Nephrotic syndrome</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">History of venous thromboembolism</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Known hypercoagulable state</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Immobilization (&lt;30 min walking per day) for &ge;3 days</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Recent travel for &gt;6 hrs</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Age &gt;60 years</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Obesity (BMI &gt;30)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Chronic venous insufficiency</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Pregnancy</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hormonal therapy (contraceptive or replacement therapy)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dehydration</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>", "more_info_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"84\" /><col width=\"84\" /><col width=\"84\" /><col width=\"196\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Geneva Score for VTE Prophylaxis</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk group</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk of VTE*</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Recommendation</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&lt;3</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Low</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0.6%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No VTE prophylaxis indicated</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ge;3</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">High</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3.2%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">VTE prophylaxis indicated</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c96466d2-fc6e-a556-c7d8-6fa0cf70b0c2\">*Composite endpoint of symptomatic VTE or VTE-related death at 90 days. From <a href=\"http://www.zlmsg.ch/uploads/media/2013_multicentre-validation-geneva-risk-score.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Nendaz 2014</a>.</span></p>", "evidence_based_medicine_en": "", "references_list": {"Original/Primary Reference": [{"href": "https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/epdf/10.1111/j.1538-7836.2006.01818.x ", "text": "Chopard P, Spirk D, Bounameaux H. Identifying acutely ill medical patients requi